Clients Controller:

localhost:8080/clients      getAllClients();    Find all Clients
localhost:8080/client/{id}      getClient();    Find client by id
localhost:8080/client          saveClient();    Save Client
localhost:8080/client/{id}   deleteClient();    Delete Client

Parcels Controller:

localhost:8080/parcels                           getAllParcels();   Find all Parcels
localhost:8080/parcelRecId/{receiverId}  getParcelToReceiverId();   Find parcel by receiverId
localhost:8080/parcelSenId/{senderId}      getParcelToSenderId();   Find parcel by receiverId
localhost:8080/parcel/{id}                           getParcel();   Find Parcel by id
localhost:8080/parcel                               saveParcel();   Save Parcel
localhost:8080/parcel/{id}                        deleteParcel();   Delete Parcel

Events Controller:

localhost:8080/events        getAllEvents();   Find all Events
localhost:8080/event/{id}        getEvent();   Find Event by id
localhost:8080/event            saveEvent();   Save Event
localhost:8080/event/{id}     deleteEvent();   Delete Event

Trackings Controller:

localhost:8080/trackings                                 getAllTracking();  Find all Trackings
localhost:8080/tracking/{id}                                getTracking();  Find Tracking by id
localhost:8080/tracking/{id}                             deleteTracking();  Delete Tracking
localhost:8080/tracking                                    saveTracking();  Save Tracking
localhost:8080/trackingsParcelNo/{parcelNo}   getAllTrackingsByParcelNo();  Find all Trackings by ParcelNo